Package: clmnis
Type: Package
Title: An R package for downloading data from the Parliamentary Members Names Information Service
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Noel",
        family = "Dempsey",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "noel.dempsey@outlook.com")
Description: This package provides functions for downloading data from the
    Parliamentary Members Names Information Service. The core functions offer simple way to
    send queries to the API endpoint and receive the results as a tibble 
    with data converted to the approriate R data type.
